item.title: Prayer bpn12448 in Namibia
item.description: Kalunga kange, omwene wange, efikilo le halo lange! Ame, omupiya woYe, onda hala oku kofa metwali lo nghenda yoYe, no ndi tu lumukwe ko mbete ya tuvikwa ne filonghenda loYe oha ndi kwindile ekwafo neameno loYe lame nenge. Ohai kwehela, Kalunga kange, eisho loYe eli ihali kofa nande,amena omesho ange aha tale umwe ehefi ove. Akoleka, hano, ove apashula amone omadidiliko oYe, atale ko mashakeneno eulu nedu lehololo loYe. Ove ou walipo komesho yo mahololo aeshe Ove omunaenghono adishe Omunanghenda ou ho kakamifa ounyuni nenghono doYe.
